{"tid":1676814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"原來fb成堆content farm網係過街老鼠鴻福郎搞既","createTime":"2019-10-26T16:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T17:17:36.000Z","uid":239696,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"15d78a1a4d4d7b8d7c27003d81d13a1dfe7acd8c","tid":1676814,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家近排都見過facebook有堆新既農場網站，<a href=\"http://乜撚news-lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B9%9C%E6%92%9Anews-lihkg.com&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=dd105fb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">乜撚news-lihkg.com</a>, <a href=\"http://hklocalpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhklocalpress.com&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=23ee3b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hklocalpress.com</a>, 成日出d假新聞。今日終於有人去trace整呢堆假網既人( <a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F126592&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=8bd2d0f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126592</a> )，堆網全部今年8月至10月開始運行，個作者trace埋背後coding。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>結果發現「香港on9協會」就係背後推手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而眾所周知個page就係鴻福郎搞既。不過淨係望住01系同on9系，都已經知係鴻福郎條撚樣搞既。原因當然就係食人血饅頭，專登整d假又煽情既新聞去呃view數搵廣告費。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image5.thenewslens.com/2019/10/lriods8jqqzia8ange3gywvckd8dzt.png?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage5.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F10%2Flriods8jqqzia8ange3gywvckd8dzt.png%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=76f73ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母鴻福郎，高連登出黎既垃圾，平時農場新聞呃9 d人「十三億人也震驚」都算，而家係到整農場新聞散假消息，食人血饅頭。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你條撚樣3年前接受蘋果訪問仲話自已唔係內容農場。<br />\n<em>專頁的宗旨，Kimochi：「在facebook按一下便開到專頁，我們不是內容農場出帖呃like 、做生意，純粹有兩個人，不是，是一班成員，擁抱這個價值和傳揚這個信念。而這次我們戴面具不是因為不能見人，是因為不想把on9定位。我相信每個香港人有on9的一面。 」<br />\n</em><a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20161228/19878596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20161228%2F19878596&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=3c429fa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20161228%2F19878596&h=9c55f742\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20161228/19878596</a><br />\n<br />\n除左香港on9協會，仲有好多page都係條撚樣開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2019/10/85qnwgla9amip17wymizwk8uxfhf0m.jpg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F10%2F85qnwgla9amip17wymizwk8uxfhf0m.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=fed3ab49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc5107ad6ec0ff87adc3fd74b7cbef538b902378","tid":1676814,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:45:06.000Z","msg":"[區議會|選戰]有個傻仔幫近千位候選人分黃藍假獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676724</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a002eed4808a41b8466346c6f44e6c1b1cc0759b","tid":1676814,"uid":280867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"屌講乜撚嘢五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676770</a>"},{"pid":"b1f31cb903955a68ddc1aa7f9edfe90ca315dd60","tid":1676814,"uid":185057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"好學唔學學支那人果套,<br />\n開一大堆垃圾