ink?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20161228%2F19878596&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=3c429fa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20161228%2F19878596&h=9c55f742\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20161228/19878596</a><br />\n<br />\n除左香港on9協會，仲有好多page都係條撚樣開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2019/10/85qnwgla9amip17wymizwk8uxfhf0m.jpg?auto=compress&amp;q=80&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F10%2F85qnwgla9amip17wymizwk8uxfhf0m.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=fed3ab49&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"認真，有冇人巴打有興趣一齊組織一個團體，去打擊content farm?"},{"pid":"81602e01ba23557ae7f65630d968944c04a7e8d0","tid":1676814,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b29174b8ec6b8333fafc7f3b1a6aa6ffee3353d7","tid":1676814,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d78a1a4d4d7b8d7c27003d81d13a1dfe7acd8c","tid":1676814,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家近排都見過facebook有堆新既農場網站，<a href=\"http://乜撚news-lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B9%9C%E6%92%9Anews-lihkg.com&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=dd105fb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">乜撚news-lihkg.com</a>, <a href=\"http://hklocalpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhklocalpress.com&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=23ee3b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hklocalpress.com</a>, 成日出d假新聞。今日終於有人去trace整呢堆假網既人( <a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/