080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2019%2F10%2F85qnwgla9amip17wymizwk8uxfhf0m.jpg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26q%3D80%26w%3D1080&h=fed3ab49&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"認真，有冇人巴打有興趣一齊組織一個團體，去打擊content farm?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:11:28.000Z","msg":"Me in"},{"pid":"e7b2ad4c16e4538a7b3eef30ed00c0ad7e3b1304","tid":1676814,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81602e01ba23557ae7f65630d968944c04a7e8d0","tid":1676814,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b29174b8ec6b8333fafc7f3b1a6aa6ffee3353d7","tid":1676814,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d78a1a4d4d7b8d7c27003d81d13a1dfe7acd8c","tid":1676814,"uid":239696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"相信大家近排都見過facebook有堆新既農場網站，<a href=\"http://乜撚news-lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B9%9C%E6%92%9Anews-lihkg.com&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=dd105fb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">乜撚news-lihkg.com</a>, <a href=\"http://hklocalpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhklocalpress.com&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=23ee3b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hklocalpress.com</a>, 成日出d假新聞。今日終於有人去trace整呢堆假網既人( <a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F126592&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=8bd2d0f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/126592</a> )，堆網全部今年8月至10月開始運行，個作者trace埋背後coding。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>結果發現「香港on9協會」就係背後推手</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而眾所周知個page就係鴻福郎搞既。不過淨係望住01系同on9系，都已經知係鴻福郎條撚樣搞既。原因當然就係食人血饅頭，專登整d假又煽情既新聞去呃view數搵廣告費。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image5.thenewslens.com/2019/10/lriods8jqqzia8ange3gywvckd8dzt